metadata.name: Ten commandments within chaos
metadata.description:
The Ten Commandments also known as the Decalogue, are a set of biblical principles relating to ethics and worship that play a fundamental role in Judaism and Christianity here are the Ten Commandments :

Piety
Love
Patience 
Reticence 
Purity 
Repose
Pacifism 
Faith
Selflessness 
Truth
